Usihlalo weDelft community policing forum uthe: "Siphoxeke kakhulu futhi asihambisani nalesi senzo sobulwane salabo okufanele bavikele baphinde bathande amantombazane amancane nabafana emiphakathini. Siyakhalisana nomndeni futhi sifuna ukuba umthetho udlale indima yawo ngalesi senzo. Siphatheke kabi kakhulu." Nangempelesonto edlule belisagobhoza igazi eKapa kubulawa abantu abawu-43.Â Abangu-13 balaba bantu babulawe endaweni yasePhilippi nokuyiyona ndawo ehamba phambili ngobugebengu kuleli dolobha. 